  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study seeks to determine whether the virus which causes COVID-19, SARS-CoV-2, is shed in
      the stools of patients who are infected.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study the stool of patients who are being treated for COVID-19 will be tested during
      treatment and then again following treatment to determine if the virus is shed in the stool
      during infection, afterwards, or both.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
