    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Signed informed consent, demonstrating that the patient understands the procedures
             required for the study and the purpose of the study

          2. Male or female of 18 years of age or older

          3. Diagnosis of COVID-19 infection by RT- PCR within 1 week of Screening

